   <collaboration id="sid-87c8b196-47b7-4ef7-92c1-5d464e5f42e3">
      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Determine if the asset needs to be retired. This could be due to the fact that a project is in place to retire the asset, amortized assets are written off the books once their book value is zero, or an inventory or reconciliation reveals that the asset is no longer in existence.  It is assumed that where assets are retired for a consideration (dollars), a project is performed and project accounting will advise the asset manager of the retirement, as well as advising accounts receivable of the receivable."/>
